title: Episode 67 - The Faulconer
description: The fellas bring in Foldi to discuss his Pulitzer story, discuss Wuhan labs, Jersey Congressman corruption and more before welcoming Mayor Kevin Faulconer to discuss his bid for Governor of CA.
